252822ee-ba37-4c57-aa9d-0612c2560ec4.title: Satisfactory
252822ee-ba37-4c57-aa9d-0612c2560ec4.summary: Satisfactory is a first-person open-world factory building game with a dash of exploration and combat. Play alone or with friends, explore an alien planet, create multi-story factories, and enter conveyor belt heaven!

bc282408-181e-4c20-8aa4-bcb6c4ce3434.title: EVE
bc282408-181e-4c20-8aa4-bcb6c4ce3434.summary: EVE Online is a free-to-play community driven space MMO where players can choose their own path from countless different options. Experience space exploration, immense PvP and PvE battles, mining, industry and a thriving player economy in an ever-expanding sandbox.
